  <official_title>Pharmacoeconomic and Clinical Prospective Comparison of PET-scan and MRI in Patients With de Novo Multiple Myeloma Less Than 65 Years of Age Treated According to IFM/DFCI 2009 Clinical Trial.</official_title>
